high_descs: Turn right, proceed to coffee table.
Pick up phone from coffee table.
Turn left, then turn right when reach couch.  Proceed to couch with box on it.
Put phone in box on couch.
Pick up box with phone in it from couch.
Turn around, proceed to chair.
Put box with phone in it on chair.
anns.task_desc: Move phone from table to box, move box with phone from couch to chair.

high_descs: Turn around and walk forward, then hang a left and walk over to the glass coffee table in the other room.
Pick up the phone off of the glass coffee table.
Turn left and walk over to the couch, then turn right and walk up to the cardboard box on the couch in front of you.
Put the phone into the cardboard box on the couch.
Pick up the cardboard box with the phone in it off of the couch.
Turn around and walk up to the chair directly in front of you.
Put the cardboard box with the phone in it on the seat of the chair.
anns.task_desc: Put a cardboard box with a phone in it on the seat of a chair.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the coffee table in the living room to the corner between the couch and the chair.
Pick up the cell phone the left side of the sculpture.
Go around the corner of the coffee table down to the end of the couch with the box on it.
Place the phone inside the box.
Pick up the box off of the couch.
Turn around and head towards the chair at the end of the coffee table.
Place the box in the middle of the cushion on the chair.
anns.task_desc: Get the remote and put into the box and move it to the chair.
